data.description: Fantastic location - 1-acre micro ranch near downtown Pescadero, elementary school, Duartes Tavern, Arcangelis Bakery, Local Coffee, Harley Farms, Taqueria, a quintessential CA coastal town. Spacious home w/office & ADU, garage, shop, equipment shed, chicken coop with/roaming area, dog run, green house & orchard of plums, apples, pears fig, berries. Wide driveway w/room for RV/boat/work trucks. Lg front lawn, mostly fenced. Backs up to big ranch. Stage Rd was stagecoach rd prior to Hwy 1.  2 miles to beach, 5 miles to redwoods.  Outdoor activities, surf, fish, hike, bike, kayak, marsh walk, bird watch. 3bd,2.5ba, living rm w/fireplace, wet bar, spacious kitchen/dining w/fireplace, family rm w/built-ins & woodstove. Bonus room/office/studio. Attached studio in-law w/woodstove. Big backyard w/brick patio & fenced lawn. Radiant heaters. Solar power-minimal PG&E. Spanish tile &wood floors. Light & views thru many windows. Great opportunity to own a coastal ranch. Buyer to verify sqare feet
